# Day 26 – Prior Authorization Workflow Simulator using Claude AI

## Objective

The objective of this task was to build an interactive Prior Authorization Workflow Simulator that demonstrates the healthcare prior authorization process through a gamified drag-and-drop experience. The application was designed to help users understand how patients, providers, and payers collaborate to obtain treatment approvals.

## Project Summary

* Application: Prior Authorization Workflow Simulator
* Technology: HTML, CSS, Vanilla JavaScript
* Type: Interactive Healthcare Workflow Simulation
* Goal: Simulate the complete Prior Authorization process in an educational and engaging way.

## Features Implemented

* Interactive drag-and-drop workflow
* Three workflow lanes: Patient, Provider, and Payer
* Multiple patient scenarios
* Medical necessity evaluation
* Prior Authorization document collection
* Payer submission workflow
* Approval, Pend, Denial, Appeal, and Peer-to-Peer Review outcomes
* Educational explanations after every stage
* Progress tracker
* Days elapsed counter
* Efficiency score
* Workflow completion summary
* Responsive interface
* Restart and New Patient functionality

## Workflow Stages

The simulator demonstrates the following workflow:

* Patient Registration
* Medical Evaluation
* Medical Necessity Review
* Document Collection
* Prior Authorization Submission
* Payer Review
* Approval / Pend / Denial Decision
* Appeal and Peer-to-Peer Review (when applicable)

## Key Learnings

* Learned how the Prior Authorization process works in the US healthcare system.
* Understood the responsibilities of patients, providers, and payers.
* Explored the importance of proper documentation and medical necessity.
* Improved interactive workflow design using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
* Learned how AI can simplify complex healthcare workflows into engaging educational simulations.

## Conclusion

This project provided valuable insights into the Prior Authorization process by converting a complex healthcare workflow into an interactive learning experience. Claude AI accelerated the development process while enhancing my understanding of healthcare operations and workflow visualization.
